Redistributed upstream data
---------------------------

This service ingests and redistributes trust and conformance data
published by the C2PA in the c2pa-org/conformance-public repository
(https://github.com/c2pa-org/conformance-public), licensed under the
Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International license (CC BY 4.0),
per that repository's LICENSE file (verified 2026-07-23).

The following data is fetched at runtime (cached for up to one hour
via the Cache API; nothing is vendored into this repository):

- trust-list/C2PA-TRUST-LIST.pem and
  trust-list/C2PA-TSA-TRUST-LIST.pem (raw.githubusercontent.com),
  used by src/index.ts for the /trust page, by
  scripts/validate-jobs.mjs as the validator trust anchors, and by
  scripts/soft-binding.mjs for TSA anchors.
- conforming-products/conforming-products-list.json
  (raw.githubusercontent.com), used by src/index.ts for the /trust
  conformance cross-reference.
- The GitHub commits Atom feeds for both paths (github.com), used by
  src/index.ts to render the change history on /trust and
  /api/trust-changes.

C2PA trust-list and conforming-products contents shown on /trust and
served through /api/trust-changes originate from that repository and
are credited to the Coalition for Content Provenance and Authenticity
(C2PA).
